    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚国会主席表示，石油公司的突发奇想可以得到控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/petro-s-whims-can-be-kept-in-check-colombia-congress-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会主席表示，哥伦比亚的机构可以抵御古斯塔沃·佩特罗总统重写宪法的企图，并绕过其他权力部门来改变国家的经济模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/petro-s-whims-can-be-kept-in-check-colombia-congress-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 19:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着立法者退出，共和党众议院多数席位进一步萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/slim-republican-house-majority-shrinks-further-as-lawmaker-quits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四届共和党国会议员迈克·加拉格尔 (Mike Gallagher) 表示，他将退出国会，从而使众议院议长迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 在 4 月 19 日开始的任何党派路线投票中只能失去一名议员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/slim-republican-house-majority-shrinks-further-as-lawmaker-quits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 19:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯顶级谷物贸易商称农业监管机构阻止出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/top-russia-grain-trader-says-exports-blocked-by-agri-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯一位顶级谷物贸易商表示，在该国农业监管机构指责其货物不符合安全和质量标准后，其小麦出口受到干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/top-russia-grain-trader-says-exports-blocked-by-agri-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 19:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大经济因临时移民新限制而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/temporary-resident-limits-are-poised-to-slow-canada-s-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家表示，加拿大计划减少临时居民，这将给未来几个月的通胀和经济增长带来下行压力，该政策明年全面生效时可能会将其人口增长率减半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/temporary-resident-limits-are-poised-to-slow-canada-s-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 18:01:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党寻求更多细节，夏威夷电力股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/hawaiian-electric-drops-as-gop-seeks-more-details-in-fire-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党人要求夏威夷电力公司回答更多问题并提供更多文件，作为调查该公用事业公司在去年致命的拉海纳野火中所扮演角色的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/hawaiian-electric-drops-as-gop-seeks-more-details-in-fire-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马乔里·泰勒·格林威胁解除约翰逊众议院议长职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/republican-greene-threatens-to-remove-johnson-as-house-speaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党众议员马乔里·泰勒·格林 (Marjorie Taylor Greene) 周五迈出了第一步，罢免了迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 众议院议长职务，并威胁称，共和党可能会在 11 月大选前再次进行改组，并引发更多内讧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/republican-greene-threatens-to-remove-johnson-as-house-speaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院在关闭截止日期前几小时通过了 1.2 万亿美元法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院在周五午夜部分政府关闭最后期限前几小时通过了一项 1.2 万亿美元的政府拨款法案，拒绝了保守派大幅削减国内支出的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在商业压力下放松跨境数据规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/china-loosens-cross-border-data-rules-to-ease-business-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国放宽了跨境数据流的监管规定，解决了外国企业的一个主要担忧，这些企业曾抱怨此前的规定扰乱了其运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/china-loosens-cross-border-data-rules-to-ease-business-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 13:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长不受富有捐助者欢迎，扩大了共和党的筹款差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/speaker-mike-johnson-s-unpopularity-with-rich-donors-widens-gop-s-cash-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在鲜为人知的众议院议长迈克·约翰逊(Mike Johnson)的领导下，众议院共和党人在竞选资金方面进一步落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/speaker-mike-johnson-s-unpopularity-with-rich-donors-widens-gop-s-cash-crunch</guid>
